title: 3437 no orange light
message:

title: 3437 no orange light
message:
Did you try another LIO flex/board?
Inspect J9500 pins for corrosion.
Check continuity for 3V42_G3H, SYS_ONEWIRE and SMC_BC_ACOK, between MLB and LIO board.

title: 3437 no orange light
message:
tried with new flex and board,
no corrosion on j9500 pins
pp3v42 - i have 3.417v
i tested continuity from j9500 to smc testpoint for sysonewire
smcbc acok -

title: 3437 no orange light
message: found the issue. smc_reset_l was giving me issues.  r5100 was half solder on the board, retinned the pad and replaced the resistor and all is working now.
